msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa uko nje ya Marekani, tunapendekeza NOWPayments (ada ndogo zaidi, moja "
"kwa moja kwenye pochi yako). Ikiwa uko Marekani, Stripe Crypto pia ni "
"chaguo. Unaweza kuwezesha huduma nyingi na kuruhusu wageni wako kuchagua!"

msgid "Enabled Payment Methods"
msgstr "Nadhani za Malipo zilizowezeshwa"

msgid ""
"Select which payment options will appear in your widget. Your visitors can "
"choose their preferred method."
msgstr ""
"Chagua chaguzi za malipo zitakazokuonekana kwenye vidokezo lako. Wageni wako"
" wanaweza kuchagua njia wanayopendelea."

