msgid ""
"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Malipo ya Stripe Crypto (USDC) yupo PATE tu kwa biashara za Marekani. Ikiwa "
"uko nje ya Marekani, Stripe itakubali malipo ya kadi ya mkopo tu kwa salio "
"lako la Stripe (si moja kwa moja kwa crypto)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa uko Marekani, unaweza kutumia Stripe kupokea crypto moja kwa moja. "
"Ikiwa uko nje, fikiria NOWPayments au CoinGate kwa malipo moja kwa moja ya "
"crypto."

