msgid ""
"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"Widget yenye nguvu, bure ya michango na malipo inayowezesha wageni wako "
"kukusaidia kwa kutumia kadi ya mikopo au sarafu za kidijitali (Quai). Hakuna"
" ada ya kila mwezi, hakuna usajili wa washirika wapitia – tu pochi yako na "
"huduma bure."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Baadhi ya kivinjari vinazuia maneno ya washirika wapitia kwa faragha. Proxy "
"hii inaweka maneno kupitia seva yako mwenyewe ili kupitikia viambatanisho "
"hivi."

msgid ""
"You can update the script URLs below if the original URLs change or if you "
"want to use a different CDN."
msgstr ""
"Unaweza kusasisha viungo vya maneno hapa chini ikiwa viungo vya awali "
"vinabadilika au ikiwa unataka kutumia CDN tofauti."

